      "text": "math.add A=9223372036854775807 B=9223372036854775807 Overflow=Promote, write to %sum%, on error set %err% = true",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Sibling of OverflowThrowSettingHonored: identical inputs, Overflow=Promote.\nlong.MaxValue \u002B long.MaxValue overflows the Long kind; under Promote the\nhandler widens Long\u2192Decimal silently and returns the sum without error.\nTogether the pair pins that the Overflow axis distinguishes outcome.",
